<div class="container headsup" id="greeter" data-id=<%= @player.id %>>
  Dear <%= @player.username %>,
</div><br><!--headsup-->

<div class="flex-container goudy" style="justify-content: space-between">
<section class="PostContent">
  <div class="flex-container-column text-boxer" style="flex-basis: 100%; justify-content: space-between">
    <p>Your skills as a poet and a writer have never been more in need. There are these things called "Payams" that are floating about, needing words to give them life.</p>
    <p>Start a <%= link_to "new Payam", new_payam_path %> and see for yourself.</p>
    <p>I thank you in advance for your help. My hope is that through your work and contributions we can all learn something.</p>
    <p>And I saw the decompose button. I pressed it. All things change and all things fade away I guess.<p>
  </div><!--flex-container-left-side-column-->
  <div class="container" id="payam-holder" data-playerId=<%=@player.id%> style="flex-basis: 100%">
    <div class="flex-container-column base-plaque">
      <% if @player.payams.completed.empty? %>
        <div class="container side-plaque">
          <div class="container" style="border-bottom: solid 2px">
            <p>Keep your eyes open here for any Payams you need to work on and any of yours that have made their journey through seven more authors.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% else %>
        <div class="container side-plaque" style="width: 100%; text-align: center">
          <div class="container" id="nexties" >
              <p class="markee">Click to see the completed payams that you worked on:</p>
              <div class="flex-container" style="justify-content: center">
                  <button class="btn btn-default" id="iron_maiden" data-id="0" onclick="firstPayam(<%= @player.id %>)">See Me</button>
              </div><!--flex-container for button-->
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <br>
      <% if !@player.waiting.empty? %>
        <div class="container side-plaque" style="width: 100%; text-align: center">
          <div class="container" style="border-bottom: solid 2px">
            <p class="markee">These payams need your help:</p>
          </div><br>
          <div id="needHelp"></div>
          <table class="dubs">
          <% @player.waiting.each do |c| %>
            <div class="flex-container top-plaque">
              <p class="dubs"><%= link_to "#{c.title}", edit_payam_path(c) %></p><p class="dubs"><em><%= link_to "ready for line #{c.counter}", edit_payam_path(c) %></em></p>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div><!--flex-container-column-->
  </div>
</div><!--flex-container-->

<div class="container headsup">
  <br>
  Yours Truly,<br>
  Payam
</div>

